description: Alterations to apartment Blocks B-E, with changes to internal layout of ground floor communal area, including increase in car parking spaces from 83 to 86 (plus 2 in tandem), increase in cycle parking spaces from 294 to 386 spaces, increase in refuse/recycling storage areas from holding 64 x 1100 l bins to 68 x 1100 l bins, 4 x 500 l and 4 x 500mm x 600mm bins and 2 x separated bulk waste storage areas, addition of water feature pump room and cleaners' store, with omission of concierge office; minor alterations to internal layouts of the 256 apartments in the consented scheme; change to mix in Block D from 48 to 45 units and Block E from 108 to 111 units, (no change to footprint of any block, or to provision of 40 No. affordable units (28 rental and 12 intermediate) in Block D, or to the overall number of dwellings or dwelling mix in the scheme); minor adjustments to the position of windows and balconies in Blocks B-E, to sizes of some balconies to meet London Plan requirements and to recessed top floor wall material and roof edge parapet details to Blocks B, C and D as non-material amendment to planning permission dated 16/10/14 ref: 14/0293/F.
